OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after ramming
OL,4,Ccar into funeral directors
OL,6,FA former police officer has been
OL,7,Fjailed for 11 years after attempting
OL,8,Fto murder his ex-girlfriend and her
OL,9,Fmother by driving a car into a funeral
OL,10,Fdirectors.
OL,12,FWilliam McBurnie, 57, previously
OL,13,Fadmitted attempting to murder the pair
OL,14,Fby driving the car at "speed" whilst
OL,15,Fnearly three times the drink drive
OL,16,Flimit through the window of the
OL,17,Ffuneral directors, to their injury and
OL,18,Fthe danger of their lives.
