OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after ramming
OL,4,Ccar into funeral directors
OL,6,FZoe Turnbull, 46, and her mother
OL,7,FBeverley Turnbull, 71, were inside the
OL,8,Fpremises in Market Place, Jedburgh,
OL,9,Fduring the incident on 7 December 2022.
OL,11,FBoth women had to take evasive action
OL,12,Fto being hit by the vehicle.
OL,14,FThe former Police Service of Northern
OL,15,FIreland officer was jailed for 11
OL,16,Fyears during his sentencing at the
OL,17,FHigh Court in Livingston on 10 October
OL,18,F2024. He pleaded guilty at the same
OL,19,Fcourt last month.
