OL,4,Ccar into funeral directors
OL,6,FJudge Lord Mulholland placed McBurnie
OL,7,Fon an extended sentence of 13 years,
OL,8,Fincluding two years of supervision on
OL,9,Fhis release from prison.
OL,11,FMcBurnie was banned from driving for
OL,12,F16-and-a-half years and issued with
OL,13,Findefinite non-harassment orders
OL,14,Fconcerning both women.
OL,16,FWelcoming the jailing of McBurnie in a
OL,17,Fstatement, Zoe Turnbull described him
OL,18,Fas the "Jekyll and Hyde of Jedburgh".
