OL,6,FShe said: "Finally, after two years of
OL,7,Fphysical, emotional and practical
OL,8,Fchaos, we have justice.
OL,10,F"I believe the attempt on my life
OL,11,Fhappened because he knew he was losing
OL,12,Fhis grip on me and this extreme act
OL,13,Fwas some warped and cowardly attempt
OL,14,Fto control things.
OL,16,F"He was just a forceful monster who
OL,17,Fencroached on our lives and used
OL,18,Fviolence to get his own way.
