OL,3,CEx-police officer jailed after ramming
OL,4,Ccar into funeral directors
OL,6,F"That man has shamed himself, the
OL,7,Fpolice service and his family -
OL,8,Fobjectively, after what he did, jail
OL,9,Freally is the only place for him.
OL,11,F"I am grateful to everyone who
OL,12,Fsupported us from the community to the
OL,13,FNHS to the police and prosecutors who
OL,14,Fput him behind bars.
OL,16,F"My mother and I now hope to put this
OL,17,Fpainful chapter behind us so we
OL,18,Frequest our privacy is respected as we
OL,19,Fmove forwards.
