OL,6,F"But as a final note I'd just like to
OL,7,Fsay to anyone suffering from domestic
OL,8,Fabuse - whether man or woman - please
OL,9,Fdo not feel like you are alone, or
OL,10,Ftrapped or have no options and please
OL,11,Fdon't wait for the worst to happen
OL,12,Fbefore acting.
OL,14,F"You have a voice and there are so
OL,15,Fmany people around you ready to listen
OL,16,F- and act ` so you can get the help
OL,17,Fyou need."
